---

<section class="pres-note">
  <div class="pres-note__container">
    <p class="pres-note__eyebrow">A note from the founder</p>
    <blockquote class="pres-note__quote">
      You made it to the end of the page, which means you are taking this seriously. So am I. For
      25 years, my name has been on every deal I have done. It is on this one. If you have one
      more question, the call goes to me or someone on my team I trust completely. Whatever you
      decide, decide it on real information.
    </blockquote>
    <div class="pres-note__sig">
      <span class="pres-note__sig-name">Joe Robert</span>
      <span class="pres-note__sig-role">Manager and Founder, Robert Ventures</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pres-note {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-note__container {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 72px 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .pres-note__eyebrow {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--green-dark);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 130%;
  }

  .pres-note__quote {
    font-family: "Roboto Serif", serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    line-height: 155%;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0 0 0 20px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--green-brand);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .pres-note__sig {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  .pres-note__sig-name {
    font-family: "Roboto Serif", serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-heading);
  }

  .pres-note__sig-role {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-body);
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 600px) {
    .pres-note__container {
      padding: 96px 32px;
    }

    .pres-note__quote {
      font-size: 26px;
    }
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 1136px) {
    .pres-note__container {
      padding: 112px 48px;
    }
  }
</style>
